/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:57:39.000Z","msg":"黃藍是政見<br />\n反茜是良知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:59:16.000Z","msg":"等睇樓主薄頭<br />\n我食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f981f7c417c91b380ce37f0e30b7c34c9d66eb","tid":2367544,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"212dc21bb9c00a2c7c64e6d205a8a276ee30fc9c","tid":2367544,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1bb9ef59076b946b3126688e07087d99e82637d","tid":2367544,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cbbf5117cbf491f92a837f33248061d0cd579f6","tid":2367544,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"不如雪巴同樓主各改一段verse同chorus啦<br />\n一段撐茜 一段反茜<br />\nbridge 再嚟一段雙方pk<br />\n應該會幾有睇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:37:47.000Z","msg":"已經反唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有咩角度可以反茜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:50:44.000Z","msg":"我9 up 下抛磚引玉<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過資料 有基因決定論一說<br />\n一係verse老作段故仔<br />\n講自己其實都想去愛上食茜<br />\n奈何自己天生基因問題 隔住個mon都聞到茜臭<br />\n<br />\n再唔係再吹大啲 話有個識左好多年嘅好兄弟<br />\n就係因為食茜問題搞到絕交<br />\n<br />\n又可以同其他出名好有爭議性嘅食物對比下<br />\ne.g. 臭豆腐、榴蓮<br />\n形容茜仲衰過佢地<br />\n<br />\n總之就正面、反面、側面、裏面、外面、行過對面，寫到啲茜有幾臭得幾臭<br />\n<br />\n以上9up 完。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:14:50.000Z","msg":"許多厭惡香菜的人會<span class=\"red\">形容它像的味道像肥皂、泥土、甚至是蟲子，對香菜表現出強烈的厭惡。</span>其實香菜的英文 &ldquo;coriander&rdquo; ，其命名字源正是希臘文中的 &ldquo;korion&rdquo;，意思就是&rdquo;蟲&rdquo;，只是現代人比起蟲子，更常聞到肥皂的味道，因此比較傾向使用肥皂味作為討厭香菜的理由。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，無論是美好的花香、柑橘香、烘烤油脂香，或是肥皂味／蟲臭味，都是<span class=\"red\">香菜所含的醛類散發出來的味道。能聞到多少，就要取決於遺傳基因了。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據分析，「癸烯醛」這種脂肪醛是香菜葉主要的香氣來源，它的<span class=\"red\">結構不穩定，容易被熱破壞，</span>所以在料理中多半都是上菜前才灑上一丁點香菜，因為要是<span class=\"red\">加熱太久，香氣就會揮發光了。</span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">認同加熱過或者浸入湯（唔濃的話），就會好淡，甚至無味</span><br />\n<br />\n研究發現其實人類身上帶有一個基因OR6A2，若是這個基因產生了變異，會使得人類對醛類化合物的嗅覺變得相當敏感，進而讓某些人天生就討厭香菜散發出帶蠟質的肥皂氣味。<br />\n<span class=\"green\">我理解有人唔食係好正常，有人唔鍾意都好正常，唔鍾意就唔鍾意無得解</span>"},{"pid":"44f47b99d7f4bf13511e5a955e900a6efbfc830e","tid":2367544,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"065db552506fce23770ca42990b60f0b9a1c3498","tid":2367544,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63642fd8deb4c0699e0582a6669758a489cdebda","tid":2367544,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c869d4a9202b4e31a1dede508f46de66dcc3164a","tid":2367544,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"中立即幫兇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"反茜任重道遠<br />\n都係將個場交返畀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"